metadata.name: The 4th of July V2
metadata.description:
Three young brothers sat together on Rockaway Beach on the 4th of July, their eyes fixated on the dazzling fireworks exploding overhead. The night sky was illuminated with bright colors of red, blue, green, and gold, and the sound of the fireworks echoed across the beach. 

The brothers sat in awe, their faces lit up with wonder and excitement, as they watched the beautiful display. They could feel the sand between their toes and the gentle ocean breeze on their faces, adding to the magic of the moment. 

As the last fireworks faded away, the brothers remained silent, soaking in the beauty of the night, and the memories they had just created.

Artist - Mike Schmidt
